<h3>Rooms</h3>

<p>
        The Purple Fox Karaoke Pub has 10 rooms available to book, all of which come
				equipped with iPads and microphones. 2 of the rooms accommodate 2 people (Fox Double),
				3 rooms accommodate 4 people (Fox Quad), 3 rooms accommodate 8 people (Fox Grande),
				and 2 rooms accommodate 12 people (Fox Enorme). The user can book a room for a specific
				time and specify the number of people who will accommodate the room. Groups can only
				book a room that is the same size as their group, unless there are no more rooms that
				accomidate their group size. In which case, they can book a room one size larger, but
				must purchase the room at full price.
</p>

<h3>Equipment</h3>
<ul>

<li>The Fox Double is equipped with 1 microphone and 1 Apple iPad</li>


<li>The Fox Quad comes equipped with 2 microphones and 2 Apple iPads</li>


<li>The Fox Grande comes equipped with 4 microphones and 4 Apple iPads</li>

<li>The Fox Ã‰norme comes equipped with 6 microphones and 6 Apple iPads</li>

</ul>

<p>
	       Each room has the fixed number of equipment, but patrons can purchase additional
				accessories during the time of their booking. The equipments include 10 microphones
				and 10 iPads that can be booked on a first-come, first-serve basis.
</p>

<h3>Booking</h3>

<p>
       Rooms can be booked from Monday thru Thursday, 4 pm to 1 am, and Friday thru Sunday,
				2 pm to 2 am.
</p>

<p>


	       Bookings can only be done once a user creates an account, and it is here that they can
				store their personal information, such as credit card number, and contant information, and
				as well view and edit their bookings. Once logged in, the user can view a calender of
				available bookings, from which they can choose a room to book, or see which rooms they've
				booked.
</p>

<h3>Cancellations</h3>
<p>
		    Cancellations that are made 4 hours before the a scheduled appointment will prevent the
				user from booking another room for 12 hours. As a result, it is recommended that
				cancellations are made a before this time period.
